item.title: Top UK Rolex Seller Rises as Outlook Eases Concern Over Tariffs
item.description: Watches of Switzerland Group Plc shares rose the most since April after the company’s outlook for the first half of its financial year eased investors’ concerns over the impact of US tariffs.
